com.tractrac.model.lib.api.route

Interface ISegment

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IAttachable, IIdentifiable, INamed

    public interface ISegment
extends INamed

    A segment is a part of an IPathRoute. It specifies the points that the segment consist of, as a line string.
